  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Civil Society Beyond Aid: Strengthening Sustainability and Strategic Collaboration among CSOs in Gha</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Operationalise the national strategy that seeks to promote the sustainability of CSOs in Ghana;
Increase ownership and relevance of the civil society directory through the documentation of data about CSOs in Ghana on an online platform; and
Facilitate networking and knowledge sharing among civil society and development partners within Ghana.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Research, collation, documentation and dissemination; 
Alliance building and networking;
Training toolkit design and the organisation of a course on CS sustainability; 
Design and launch a nationwide / regional sustainability advocacy campaign for CSOs; and
Follow up activities that will be necessary to achieve the key objectives.</narrative>
  </description>
